  "sections": [
    {
      "id": "SEC1",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "SAP TM Deployment Options"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "SAP Transportation Management can be deployed in different architectures depending on business size, complexity and integration requirements. Organizations can implement SAP TM as Embedded TM within SAP S/4HANA or as a Standalone TM system."
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC3",
      "type": "callout",
      "calloutType": "important",
      "title": "Key Concept",
      "content": "Embedded TM is recommended for most SAP S/4HANA customers, while Standalone TM is generally used for large enterprises requiring advanced transportation planning."
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC4",
      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Deployment Models"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC5",
      "type": "table",
      "title": "SAP TM Deployment Types",
      "headers": [
        "Deployment",
        "Description"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "Embedded TM",
          "Transportation Management built directly into SAP S/4HANA."
        ],
        [
          "Standalone TM",
          "Independent SAP TM system integrated with ERP."
        ],
        [
          "Cloud Deployment",
          "SAP-hosted cloud environment."
        ],
        [
          "Hybrid Deployment",
          "Combination of on-premise and cloud systems."
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
